									<children>
										<node id="data" key="key">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The woman stands up from her crouched position at the stall, holding her bag of pickings - we suddenly cut back to the grim reality. The woman, dressed in rags and sporting bloodied hands, carries an armful of rubble. She turns to join a line of other enslaved baldurians, including the child we saw with the ball, now replaced by a large stone. Around them, the city looks grey and foreboding, with some buildings in ruin, and piles of rubble lying about for repurposing. Some mind flayers hover nearby, supervising." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
